 Speaking to TshisaLIVE Kelly s PR manager Linda Moeketsi confirmed that the songstress had bagged a new show called Love and Matrimony on DSTV. It will be a new platform and environment for me and I look forward to hearing all the love stories good or bad. If we all have one thing in common it is the yearn for love whether we admit it or not Kelly told Drum magazine.Kelly will profile some of SA s most famous faces about their love life marriage break-ups and challenges that they ve faced in their relationships.Love and Matrimony airs at the end June 2017 on GauTV DSTV channel 265.